{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775879037464,"sessionID":"ses_2855dd4b1ffeqb6215FEQBMdF3","part":{"id":"prt_d7aa23cb4001UzfvnBRx54Sd1b","messageID":"msg_d7aa22c2a001iBJCOnWNRH9cwT","sessionID":"ses_2855dd4b1ffeqb6215FEQBMdF3","type":"tool","tool":"task","callID":"toolu_7e6e7a89d1714ce9b760b118","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"description":"Explore agentcube project","prompt":"Explore the agentcube project structure to understand:\n1. The overall project structure\n2. How integrations are implemented (look for existing integration modules)\n3. Any existing Dify-related code or references\n4. The tasks.md format/pattern used in this project\n5. Check for any specs or design documents related to AR-036 or Dify integration\n\nSearch thoroughly and report back with:\n- Project root structure\n- Location of integrations module\n- Any existing integration patterns\n- Any AR-036 or Dify related files found\n- Examples of tasks.md files if they exist","subagent_type":"explore"},"output":"task_id: ses_2855db62fffeDKGLwgOt2ZM5ex (for resuming to continue this task if needed)\n\n<task_result>\nNow I have a comprehensive understanding of the project. Let me provide a complete summary:\n\n---\n\n## AgentCube Project Structure Analysis\n\n### 1. Overall Project Structure\n\nThe agentcube project is located at `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/` with the following key directories:\n\n```\nagentcube/\n├── agentcube/          # Python SDK & CLI\n├── cmd/                # Go binaries (router, workload-manager, agentd, picod)\n├── pkg/                # Go packages (apis, client, router, workloadmanager, etc.)\n├── integrations/      # Integration modules (contains design.md & spec.md)\n├── changes/           # Change requests (AR-001 through AR-036)\n├── python-sdk/        # Python SDK documentation\n├── docker/            # Dockerfiles\n├── .github/           # GitHub workflows\n├── tests/             # Test files\n├── design.md          # Main design document (large)\n├── proposal.md        # Current AR proposal\n├── tasks.md           # Root level tasks (AR-032)\n└── project.md         # Project context/overview\n```\n\n### 2. Integrations Module Location\n\n**Path**: `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/integrations/`\n\nContains:\n- `design.md` - Design document with Dify plugin file map and structure\n- `spec.md` - Normative specifications for integrations\n\n### 3. Integration Patterns\n\nThe project follows a pattern where:\n- **design.md** contains file structures, YAML schemas, and code examples\n- **spec.md** contains Gherkin-style requirements (SHALL, SHOULD, MAY language)\n- Integrations use Python with specific frameworks (Dify plugin uses `dify-plugin` SDK)\n- Configuration is typically done via YAML files (manifest.yaml, provider YAMLs, tool YAMLs)\n\n### 4. Dify-Related Files Found\n\n**AR-036 (Dify 插件集成) Change Request**:\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-036/proposal.md` - Proposal document\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-036/design.md` - Design template (mostly TODO)\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-036/delta-spec.md` - Detailed delta specification (458 lines)\n\n**Reference locations mentioned** (not present in workspace):\n- `/tmp/agentcube-ref/integrations/dify-plugin/` - Reference Dify plugin implementation\n- `/tmp/agentcube-ref/example/pcap-analyzer/` - Reference PCAP analyzer example\n\n**Integration design docs**:\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/integrations/design.md` - Contains Dify plugin file map, manifest structure, provider/tool YAML structures\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/integrations/spec.md` - Contains normative requirements for Dify plugin integration\n\n### 5. Tasks.md Format/Pattern\n\nThe tasks.md format follows this structure:\n\n```markdown\n# AR-XXX: [Title]\n\n**Module:** [module name]  \n**Language:** [language]  \n**Size:** [S/M/L]  \n**Design Stage:** [ST-X completed]\n\n---\n\n## Phase N: [Phase Name]\n\n- [x] **T001** Task description (completed)\n- [ ] **T002** Task description (pending)\n\n## Dependencies\n\n| Task | Depends On | Description |\n|------|------------|-------------|\n| T001 | - | Setup |\n| T002 | T001 | Next step |\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n\n- [x] Criterion 1\n- [ ] Criterion 2\n```\n\nFound in multiple locations:\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/tasks.md` (AR-032)\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-0XX/tasks.md` (for each AR)\n\n### 6. Files to Create for AR-036 (from delta-spec.md)\n\nThe delta-spec.md specifies these files should be created:\n\n```\nintegrations/dify-plugin/\n├── main.py                           # Plugin entry: Plugin(DifyPluginEnv(MAX_REQUEST_TIMEOUT=120)).run()\n├── manifest.yaml                     # Plugin manifest (version 0.0.2)\n├── provider/\n│   ├── agentcube.yaml               # Provider descriptor\n│   └── agentcube.py                 # AgentcubeCodeInterpreterProvider class\n├── tools/\n│   ├── agentcube-code-interpreter.yaml  # Tool parameter schema\n│   └── agentcube-code-interpreter.py    # AgentcubeCodeInterpreterTool class\n├── requirements.txt                  # dify-plugin>=0.4.2,<0.5.0, agentcube-sdk>=0.0.10\n├── GUIDE.md, README.md, PRIVACY.md  # Documentation\n├── .difyignore                      # Dify ignore file\n├── icon.png, icon-dark.png          # Plugin icons\n\nexample/pcap-analyzer/\n├── pcap_analyzer.py                 # FastAPI app\n├── requirements.txt                 # Dependencies\n├── Dockerfile                       # Container build\n├── deployment.yaml                  # K8s deployment\n└── README.md\n```\n\n### Key Dependencies Identified\n\n- **dify-plugin**: >=0.4.2,<0.5.0\n- **agentcube-sdk**: >=0.0.10\n- **Python**: 3.12 (for the plugin runner)\n</task_result>","metadata":{"sessionId":"ses_2855db62fffeDKGLwgOt2ZM5ex","model":{"modelID":"MiniMax-M2.5","providerID":"bailian-coding-plan"},"truncated":false},"title":"Explore agentcube project","time":{"start":1775878949325,"end":1775879037462}}}}
